Class TimeService

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.sakaiproject.time.cover.TimeService
  • Deprecated. 
    Static covers should not be used in favour of injection or lookup via the component manager. This cover will be removed in a later version of the Kernel

    public class TimeService
extends Object

    TimeService is a static Cover for the TimeService; see that interface for usage details.
